text.tspan: An abstracted representation of a typical sequence of 3 transactions
in a tumbler run. Each utxo or set of utxos as input or output is marked
with a 'C' variable representing the completed mixdepth closure it belongs
to. TX2 is a sweep as evidenced by the lack of the third change output to C1.
CMC C1 is owned by the same entity as CMC C3 with high probability.
